---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Disclaimer"
  description="Wander Tiger affiliate, advertising, and financial content disclaimer."
  current="none"
>
  <section class="hero-panel nes-container is-dark with-title">
    <p class="title">DISCLAIMER</p>
    <p class="nes-text is-disabled kicker">FINANCE · AFFILIATES · ADS</p>
    <h1 class="nes-text is-primary page-title hero-title">IMPORTANT NOTES</h1>
    <p class="nes-text hero-copy">
      Wander Tiger is a personal documentation site about AI, agentic workflows,
      trading systems, and personal finance experiments.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="nes-container is-dark with-title section-gap">
    <p class="title">FINANCIAL CONTENT</p>
    <div class="console-list">
      <div class="console-row">
        <span class="console-index">01</span>
        <p class="nes-text is-disabled">
          Content on this website is for educational and documentary purposes
          only. It is not financial advice, investment advice, trading advice,
          or a recommendation to buy, sell, or hold any security.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="console-row">
        <span class="console-index">02</span>
        <p class="nes-text is-disabled">
          Trading options and other financial instruments involves risk. Past
          performance, trade journals, and research notes do not guarantee future
          results.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="console-row">
        <span class="console-index">03</span>
        <p class="nes-text is-disabled">
          Always do your own research and consider seeking advice from a licensed
          professional before making financial decisions.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="nes-container is-dark with-title section-gap">
    <p class="title">AFFILIATES & ADS</p>
    <p class="nes-text is-disabled compact-copy">
      Wander Tiger may use affiliate links, referral links, display ads, or
      sponsorships in the future. If you click an affiliate link and make a
      purchase, I may earn a commission at no extra cost to you.
    </p>
    <p class="nes-text is-disabled compact-copy">
      Affiliate or advertising relationships do not determine the core project
      documentation. The goal is to list tools and services that are relevant to
      the actual build journey.
    </p>
  </section>
</Layout>
